description:
Metallica - City Of Rock, Rio de Janeiro(2-CD)ak320

The City of Rock (Cidade do Rock), located in Barra da Tijuca, Rio de Janeiro, is an events venue best known for hosting Rock in Rio.

This was the fourth time that Metallica performed in Rio de Janeiro.
Metallica last played Rio on September 25, 2011.
This was the first time that "Hit the Lights," "Holier Than Thou" and "The Day That Never Comes" were performed in Rio.
Metallica performed 19 songs off of 8 albums: Kill 'Em All (3), Ride the Lightning (5), Master of Puppets (3), ...And Justice for All (2), Metallica (3), Load(1), Reload (1), Death Magnetic (1)
